    "name": "Avenger Dedication",
    "prerequisite": "*Avenger*",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "Your training regimen has given you particular advantages when it comes to enforcing the interests of your faith. You gain a +1 status bonus to saving throws against divine spells and effects that deal spirit damage. You can use Religion to Coerce, Gather Information, or Track as long as you are in a town or city with a church dedicated to your deity, extracting clues from the faithful with displays of your piety.",
